{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [195.5, 761.28, 1518.1000000000001, 1063.84], "block_id": "051-006", "elapsed_sec": 1.137, "error": "", "label": "Text", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 51, "page_label": "051", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 6, "record_id": "block:051:051-006:f6728710156b979c26b43f996760b62ca8da8ebab3cf93b5a7eac1c65c3c5597", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-045.png", "source_sha256": "f6728710156b979c26b43f996760b62ca8da8ebab3cf93b5a7eac1c65c3c5597", "source_text": "新しい呪文を覚えようと精神を集中させていたティケは、背後から近寄ってきたインキュバスに気がつかなかった。部屋の扉はすべて閉めきってはいたが、ウィーザード・ロックまではしていなかった。大抵のモンスターが相手なら、最初の一撃は喰らったところですぐに気づき、反撃をすることができる。", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "Tike was concentrating on trying to learn a new spell and did not notice the Incubus approaching from behind. Although all the doors in the room were closed, they had not been wizard-locked. If most monsters were the对手方，第一击被吃下后，通常可以立即察觉并反击。[OCR? REACT?]"}
