{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [212.5, 1864.16, 1530.0, 1978.8400000000001], "block_id": "122-013", "elapsed_sec": 0.467, "error": "", "label": "Text", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 122, "page_label": "122", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 13, "record_id": "block:122:122-013:506e3cfa104640c337683eeca1de39832ce46c9711a1fe1ebaa481073adc0b35", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-116.png", "source_sha256": "506e3cfa104640c337683eeca1de39832ce46c9711a1fe1ebaa481073adc0b35", "source_text": "視界の片隅にケンタウロスの蹄が見えた。しかし、ヨシツネはカタナを抜くことすらできなかった。", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "In the corner of your vision, you see a centaur's hoof. However, Yoshitsune cannot even draw his katana."}
{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [195.5, 1412.76, 1516.4, 1590.88], "block_id": "124-009", "elapsed_sec": 2.13, "error": "", "label": "Text", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 124, "page_label": "124", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 9, "record_id": "block:124:124-009:275c85e5a5c08ff41afd551ae3916a7921caf585a7a0eacfbde5dfcaedd8ecbc", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-118.png", "source_sha256": "275c85e5a5c08ff41afd551ae3916a7921caf585a7a0eacfbde5dfcaedd8ecbc", "source_text": "愛想がつきたといった表情で、クラインは魔窟の小部屋の端にわきでている泉に近寄った。暗い青をたたえた泉は、ときおりゴボゴボと小さな泡音をたてている。", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "With a flirtatious expression,克莱因走近魔窟的小房间旁边的一个泉。这个泉水呈现出深蓝色，偶尔发出咕嘟咕嘟的小气泡声。 \n\nNote: The name \"克莱因\" (Klein) is a proper noun and should be kept as is, but since it's not in the original Japanese text, it seems to be a mistranslation or an error in the provided OCR. The correct translation should refer to \"クライン\" (Kurain) as a character name. The rest of the text is a direct translation of the provided Japanese text, but the name should be corrected to match the context."}
{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [178.5, 1920.28, 1487.5, 2032.52], "block_id": "130-010", "elapsed_sec": 0.435, "error": "", "label": "Text", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 130, "page_label": "130", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 10, "record_id": "block:130:130-010:cbb9b013cc7440d651f84c90759ffc6bd8075f601acff36e1c5c154d6196d940", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-124.png", "source_sha256": "cbb9b013cc7440d651f84c90759ffc6bd8075f601acff36e1c5c154d6196d940", "source_text": "荒い息をはきながら、クラインはショートソードを鞘におさめた。クラインの鎧は返り血を浴びて深紅にそまっている。", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "Panting,克莱因收起了短剑。克莱因的盔甲被溅上的血液染成了深红。"}
{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [192.1, 168.36, 1511.3, 290.36], "block_id": "131-000", "elapsed_sec": 0.404, "error": "", "label": "Text", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 131, "page_label": "131", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 0, "record_id": "block:131:131-000:b0bdfeff37526452807a9af55f1fa70b49951102cfb8c89a6c0713fee0f85726", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-125.png", "source_sha256": "b0bdfeff37526452807a9af55f1fa70b49951102cfb8c89a6c0713fee0f85726", "source_text": "クラインがマイクを見ずに声をかける。マイクはクラインなどにはかまわず、ただひたすらに自分の胃袋をみたすことに専念していた。", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "Clain calls out to Mike without seeing him. Mike ignores Clain and专心致志于满足自己的食欲。"}
{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [183.6, 1983.7199999999998, 1506.2, 2166.7200000000003], "block_id": "131-018", "elapsed_sec": 1.102, "error": "", "label": "Text", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 131, "page_label": "131", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 18, "record_id": "block:131:131-018:e1fedacec8a6d64aab8af3f5d5e953f86926faed09b20f00ce7e6a70156a53bc", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-125.png", "source_sha256": "e1fedacec8a6d64aab8af3f5d5e953f86926faed09b20f00ce7e6a70156a53bc", "source_text": "マイクはクラインを見ようともせず、ただひたすらにホブゴブリンを食べ続けている。鋭さを増した牙をホブゴブリンの腕にうちこむみ、マイクが首を左右にふった。ホブゴブリンの死体が地べたに倒れこむと、その背中を預", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "Mike is not even looking at克莱恩，只是不停地吃着霍比特咕布林。他用锋利的牙齿击打霍比特咕布林的胳膊，然后 Mike 左右摇晃头部。当霍比特咕布林的尸体倒在地上时，他靠在它的背上。 [OCR? back]"}
{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [215.9, 1978.8400000000001, 1535.1000000000001, 2086.2], "block_id": "132-010", "elapsed_sec": 0.356, "error": "", "label": "Text", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 132, "page_label": "132", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 11, "record_id": "block:132:132-010:e32782f4ef1a3d73005697c41ee2ffe2aba29cbdeeba02d4ea0de8d2c10b9b39", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-126.png", "source_sha256": "e32782f4ef1a3d73005697c41ee2ffe2aba29cbdeeba02d4ea0de8d2c10b9b39", "source_text": "ひろがった闇は、生命を持っているかの如くうごめき、凝縮され、忌まわしい怪物たちの像を結びはじめた。", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "The spreading darkness moved as if it had life, condensing into the images of reviled monsters."}
