{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [234.60000000000002, 1637.24, 1547.0, 1810.48], "block_id": "152-012", "elapsed_sec": 0.642, "error": "", "label": "Text", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 152, "page_label": "152", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 12, "record_id": "block:152:152-012:411dad523e8447302c5b9d19fde4526be88324c0c6ccfb3e935de9bd4a0e2242", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-146.png", "source_sha256": "411dad523e8447302c5b9d19fde4526be88324c0c6ccfb3e935de9bd4a0e2242", "source_text": "このマントを羽織った者は、自分の姿が見えなくなることに気がつくだろう。そう、このマントは透明化の呪文を封じたものなのだ。しかし、防御力そのものは期待できない。", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "Wearing this cloak, one will notice that their own form becomes invisible. Indeed, this cloak封印了透明化的咒语。然而，其防御力本身是不可靠的。"}
{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [258.4, 1759.24, 1519.8, 1808.04], "block_id": "154-008", "elapsed_sec": 0.243, "error": "", "label": "Text", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 154, "page_label": "154", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 11, "record_id": "block:154:154-008:33916b3654bd09c4c9e7e563944d8b1dbec2748a67e044457e46cfc7b493b6c8", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-148.png", "source_sha256": "33916b3654bd09c4c9e7e563944d8b1dbec2748a67e044457e46cfc7b493b6c8", "source_text": "ごく普通の兜。これといって特徴がないのが特徴といえるかもしれない。", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "A普通的头盔。也许可以说它的特点就是没有特点。"}
