{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [185.3, 1237.08, 1506.2, 1346.88], "block_id": "193-013", "elapsed_sec": 0.424, "error": "", "label": "Text", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 193, "page_label": "193", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 13, "record_id": "block:193:193-013:d8319587d8061c1405b8feab73b423ab192c1d594d92017d70ecb887e5db0430", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-187.png", "source_sha256": "d8319587d8061c1405b8feab73b423ab192c1d594d92017d70ecb887e5db0430", "source_text": "エルフ造りの美しい装飾が施された短剣。ホビットら、剣を使うには背が足りない種族が好んで使用する。", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "A beautifully decorated short sword crafted by elves. Used by races like hobbits who are too short to use swords effectively."}
{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [204.0, 771.04, 1518.1000000000001, 883.28], "block_id": "196-007", "elapsed_sec": 0.463, "error": "", "label": "Text", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 196, "page_label": "196", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 7, "record_id": "block:196:196-007:a3a4fe47ed31da3c63842d7e05056179a30760a62773a4a1370a331948765e24", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-190.png", "source_sha256": "a3a4fe47ed31da3c63842d7e05056179a30760a62773a4a1370a331948765e24", "source_text": "つるはし状の斧。背の低いドワーフたちが力任せに振るうときに、とてつもない威力を誇るという。", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "Pickaxe. It boasts tremendous power when wielded by矮人，who are short in stature and swing it with brute force."}
{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [195.5, 851.56, 1514.7, 966.24], "block_id": "206-009", "elapsed_sec": 0.778, "error": "", "label": "Text", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 206, "page_label": "206", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 9, "record_id": "block:206:206-009:e3aa4ed0fd39ca87c8102264a6d61c954b38b8e598f9c7a507038bb82d0b1cc3", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-200.png", "source_sha256": "e3aa4ed0fd39ca87c8102264a6d61c954b38b8e598f9c7a507038bb82d0b1cc3", "source_text": "生命の力——太陽の輝きをその刀身に封じ込んだという長剣。死の領域にその生の根源を持つ生物に対して、無上の力を誇るのは当然といえよう。", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "A sword imbued with the power of life—its blade sealed with the glow of the sun. It is natural for a being with its origin in the realm of life to boast supreme power against those in the domain of death."}
{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [1336.2, 990.6400000000001, 1519.8, 1032.12], "block_id": "206-011", "elapsed_sec": 0.102, "error": "", "label": "Text", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 206, "page_label": "206", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 11, "record_id": "block:206:206-011:4ddeb710095c77b9214f0a6d847c15eb6ab0008f776455efb94f2d94f40f453f", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-200.png", "source_sha256": "4ddeb710095c77b9214f0a6d847c15eb6ab0008f776455efb94f2d94f40f453f", "source_text": "つらぬき丸", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "Piercing丸"}
{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [601.8, 2242.36, 1205.3, 2286.28], "block_id": "241-013", "elapsed_sec": 0.293, "error": "", "label": "PageFooter", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 241, "page_label": "241", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 13, "record_id": "block:241:241-013:e13bed8b71acd6b1320dcf24a3ab84c99138defd104e360b75da62f73d719a77", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-235.png", "source_sha256": "e13bed8b71acd6b1320dcf24a3ab84c99138defd104e360b75da62f73d719a77", "source_text": "巨獣、ネズミ、岩モグラ、蜘蛛、蠍、潜む者", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "巨型兽、老鼠、石鼬、蜘蛛、蝎子、潜行者"}
{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [198.9, 161.04000000000002, 1519.8, 534.36], "block_id": "258-000", "elapsed_sec": 1.521, "error": "", "label": "Text", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 258, "page_label": "258", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 0, "record_id": "block:258:258-000:b3ed3952990989727ecf4b2448c7035101cfbe1573d69fa5a3bc7b83806e9084", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-252.png", "source_sha256": "b3ed3952990989727ecf4b2448c7035101cfbe1573d69fa5a3bc7b83806e9084", "source_text": "「自分の属する神の祭壇に供物を捧げることだ。倒した怪物どもの死体を捧げつづけるんだ。供物がでかければでかいだけ、強力であればあるだけ見返りも大きい。四つ葉のクローバーが落ちてくれば、供物を気に入ってもらえたということだ。そうしていけば神の恩寵を得ることができる。そう、神と語らうこともできるし、銘刀すら神から賜わることがあるらしいぞ。俺にはそんな恩寵はなかったがな」", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "\"Offer sacrifices to the altar of your deity. Continue offering the bodies of the monsters you slay. The larger and more powerful the sacrifice, the greater the回报 will be. If four-leaf clovers start appearing, it means the sacrifice has been accepted. By doing this, you can gain the favor of the deity. You can even communicate with the deity, and legendary weapons may be bestowed by the deity. I didn't receive such favor, though.\""}
{"base_url": "http://127.0.0.1:8001/v1", "bbox": [1030.2, 295.24, 1514.7, 339.16], "block_id": "271-001", "elapsed_sec": 0.291, "error": "", "label": "Text", "max_tokens": 700, "model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "page": 271, "page_label": "271", "passthrough_non_cjk": false, "reading_order": 1, "record_id": "block:271:271-001:f83d39cf229e7cca8a4594f28b0bcf2d1d5e5956f2700a10f0acffd4915ac2a0", "record_type": "block", "source_image": "cropped_nethack_uncropped_both_sides_ordered-265.png", "source_sha256": "f83d39cf229e7cca8a4594f28b0bcf2d1d5e5956f2700a10f0acffd4915ac2a0", "source_text": "1993年・4・1 蓮川龍司郎", "status": "ok", "temperature": 0.0, "translation": "1993年・4・1 Ryojiro Tanikawa"}
